    "text": "Travel Optimization by Updating and Revitalizing Infrastructure to Support Mobilization Act or the TOURISM Act\n\nThis bill changes requirements for and contents of the National Travel and Tourism Infrastructure Strategic Plan. The changes include requiring the plan to address strategies to leverage infrastructure investments to support the travel and tourism economy in the wake of the COVID-19 pandemic."
